{"tid":233020,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［年經/公投］端午節食傻你鍾意配白砂糖定豉油","createTime":"2017-05-07T08:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T02:25:22.000Z","uid":30453,"like":111,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6942062af4de29d0d46e1a0b129d0c819009c6b4","tid":233020,"uid":30453,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.swaindestinations.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Dragon-Boat-Festival-03_tourismboard.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.swaindestinations.com%2Fblog%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F06%2FDragon-Boat-Festival-03_tourismboard.jpg&h=1ac15432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又到咗端午節<br />\n主角當然係放假同食傻<br />\n龍舟同屈原都只係輔助<br />\n<img src=\"http://cul.china.com.cn/photo/images/attachement/jpg/site449/20140530/406186eabb5714f26ac05d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcul.china.com.cn%2Fphoto%2Fimages%2Fattachement%2Fjpg%2Fsite449%2F20140530%2F406186eabb5714f26ac05d.JPG&h=3cda25bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而食傻嗰時就有個世紀難題<br />\n究竟應該點糖定豉油<br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-mNIwlm8xaHA/VWnRIqkC9EI/AAAAAAAABUY/fVu9P7gVA98/s1600/20150523_212802.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-mNIwlm8xaHA%2FVWnRIqkC9EI%2FAAAAAAAABUY%2FfVu9P7gVA98%2Fs1600%2F20150523_212802.jpg&h=02eb85be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個時候得四個選擇：糖 豉油 不了 whynotboth<br />\n身為一個真毒真男人<br />\n係呢個重要時刻係唔會退縮<br />\n更加唔會一腳踏兩船<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/j4vkziw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj4vkziw.gif&h=6c609c26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就係白砂糖派嘅<br />\n最鍾意食咸肉傻點砂糖<br />\n糖嘅甜同咸蛋黃豬肉嘅咸形成強烈嘅對比<br />\n兩種味道互相輝映<br />\n而我最鍾意食嘅其實係傻入邊嘅綠豆<br />\n最憎紅豆傻<br />\n人大咗老咗食一兩隻已經頂唔順<br />\n同埋唔想食個蛋黃<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 白砂糖<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.99.com.cn/uploads/160615/395_111329_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.99.com.cn%2Fuploads%2F160615%2F395_111329_1.jpg&h=c4728206&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 豉油<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn-blog.ytower.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/IMG_7747-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn-blog.ytower.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F06%2FIMG_7747-1.jpg&h=f5d17ab9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92f274dc4018291ea552288bf6d836ab7852010b","tid":233020,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"揀水傻 點 砂糖<br />\n其他拎去喂狗"},{"pid":"be56731d50fc5c480ee43e4dc5ecc6e3f76e7e91","tid":233020,"uid":2611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"食傻一定係砂糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3b1c06fc59f78ad8405424c97dde0bb50fa94c","tid":233020,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"辣椒仔Tabasco"},{"pid":"fcd51f35af342fc728d8c76c3c22c8364779e0d4","tid":233020,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揀水傻 點 砂糖<br />\n其他拎去喂狗</blockquote><br />\n傻仔先食簡水種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8135d4c716f29324a577bb5ee7ddbad88b6b59b","tid":233020,"uid":17881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>揀水傻 點 砂糖<br />\n其他拎去喂狗</blockquote><br />\n傻仔先食簡水種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常拎去餵狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea5ae88686672b9a964b68ad2f3b0f59f5b32de","tid":233020,"uid":104500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"對唔住啊我係白砂糖加豉油架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d30f18dcc